{"type": "article", "id": 54839, "title": "梯形立柱支撑的鸟笼柜，也可做空间隔断｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-07-02T23:05:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 51509, "name": "Magisso"}, {"id": 51510, "name": "NUB"}, {"id": 51511, "name": "Slim Design"}, {"id": 51512, "name": "肆社家具"}, {"id": 51513, "name": "Simo Lahtinen"}, {"id": 51514, "name": "Miguel Herranz"}, {"id": 51515, "name": "Stéphanie Marin"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 104, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180702232910BqA3lSeGt9RWFj5D.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; background-color: #ffffff} span.s6 {font-kerning: none; color: #545454; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #545454} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>鸟笼柜 by 肆社家具 </h3><p>设计师原创家具品牌“肆社家具”推出新作鸟笼柜，梯形立柱，简洁而富有韵律感。鸟笼柜是一次多材料结合的设计，黑胡桃木与樱桃木的质地细腻柔美，设计师运用其本色，造成对比效果，凸显了支撑线条。</p><p>鸟笼柜不同于普通柜体那样四腿支撑，而是一系列立柱线条。为了达到视觉上较为轻盈的效果，立柱做了梯型的设计，不影响结构受力的情况下，正视效果更为纤细立体。柜体双面镜像立柱线条，弱化了柜体的正反面区分，使其更可以作为空间隔断使用。售价 14800 元起，<a href=\"https://item.taobao.com/item.htm?spm=a1z10.5-c-s.w4002-17780268779.23.545832a8s9B1zG&amp;id=564797720018\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702232954jSX7vMeFzbTAUfdw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.742479\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702232955cQaJXhmzRY1ywlAE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.497780\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702232958ZAb8faI9Je6RkyvU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.497988\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702233000X9oebBijKzrJdpZC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.691333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702233003jGITxu0WNJUfVAoz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498197\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702233011xZW1c0tKPudAHmEG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.717333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702233011JpPXEbT86cok5ZYG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713702\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>La Barricade by Stéphanie Marin</h3><p>法国设计师 Stephanie Marin 的作品常给人将艺术和设计融合的感觉。最近，她为其自有品牌 Smarin 设计了新作公共座椅装置 La Barricade，灵感来源于沙袋路障。</p><p>乍一看，La Barricade 就是随意叠放的一堆豆袋式靠垫，可以平面铺开，也可以堆叠起来，任由用户爬上去或是陷入其中。垫子由灰色亚麻织物制成，内部是填充纤维棉。当用户陷入其中时，还能提供一定程度的隔音效果。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018070223304589LpPsKwjeVFQvZM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702233048nQlstXy8LU0C9aFh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702233048GdoZ5ELKByrWRzf6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702233049Q9B2K6fC7aXtyPU4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702233049esGHK01WNODwEXg6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/07/02/smarin-seating-la-barricade-design/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Essence &amp; Flow &amp; Errosion by Miguel Herranz</h3><p>西班牙设计师 Miguel Herranz，以自然石材为主材，利用机器人加工系统，制造出一系列有机形状的洗手池 Essence，Flow 和 Errosion，充分展现出石块的自然特质，包括产自萨拉格萨的金丝黑色石材、产自布尔戈斯的灰色石材，以及意大利卡拉拉白色大理石。</p><p>给予设计师灵感的是石头与水。Essence 系列突出展示了天然石材的力量感和体量感。Flow 系列体量较小，重量较轻，是小空间的理想选择。Errosion 系列则让人联想到流水状态的雕塑形态。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702233137Qoqy96iZePhEKY71.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702233137qeEOX31698TArKPn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702233137a1dlcigMqPKOZV0Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702233137vTmIMP8Ecog6Lb7p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702233137i0nL9xj5X26BuStR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807022331375nKTeMZpAE4D3jxz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/design/miguel-herranz-robotic-machining-natural-stone-sink-collection-nerinea-07-01-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designboom</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>BAGTAG device by Slim Design</h3><p>荷兰初创公司 BAGTAG 针对日渐拥挤的机场，推出了一款智能化解决方案，它设有一个电子纸显示器，可以通过蓝牙连接到智能手机，查看行李状态。</p><p>BAGTAG 取代了传统的纸质标签，它可以使用 VHB 粘合剂贴在行李箱上。目前，BAGTAG 的相关应用程序，已经可以服务于汉莎航空、瑞士和澳大利亚航空公司的乘客。售价 89 欧元，<a href=\"https://bagtag.com/products/bagtag\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702233219xNUP8y3aK2VMLS6D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.361111\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702233219U8W5Abf90lxCQL76.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702233219XG7YcZ0RDwj89HWi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671149\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702233219XpiOahqmYy2exH1z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702233219onAbaxt3m0Qz8URI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702233219ALbFWMNm830V1JfI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>N1 collection by NUB</h3><p>N1 腕表是伦敦设计团队 NUB 的第一款作品，目前正在众筹平台 Kickstarter 上募资。深色喷砂表盘，搭配黄色秒针，像是在一幅极简主义画作上落下的大胆一笔。</p><p>表盘上的条形凹陷处形成刻度，同样颜色的时针和分针悬停在上方，6 点钟位置还设有日期窗口。而手表的表冠位于 2 点钟位置，创造出轻微的不平衡感。早鸟价 150 英镑，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/nubwatches/nub-watches-swiss-precision-and-british-engineerin\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702233330L42MiTJfdqXvHkUm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702233330ErTtGLjFiW8DR24A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702233330VHn7ErC856yIpRtD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807022333310CPMaIJiDh2YpLvH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.647619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702233331gX57bUpVQTBtMfKh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807022333316UcZmn4tzxsAuMfl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807022333329Setq62U7o5OCYcx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Element No.1 table by Simo Lahtinen for Magisso</h3><p>Maggiso 是一个实现北欧设计、创新的芬兰年轻品牌。最近，居住在阿姆斯特丹的芬兰工业设计师Simo Lahtinen 为其设计了一款名为 Element No.1 的小边桌，充分考虑到其移动和安装时的便携性。它有一个易于提拉的手柄，可以轻松在房间内移动。所有部件都由单一的平板构成，组装简单。售价 149 欧元，<a href=\"https://www.ikarus.de/element-no-1-beistelltisch.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702233411Rn7uLJhVa4BEKPlY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.952381\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702233411kOz3dBYEMHF1nN0T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702233411qQJX68MsU5v4k1Ec.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.952381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702233412JqfWsPLQaUpy913K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702233412FhG9AX548oCIcyEl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.653333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702233412RS4E9Dh5vyM78dLj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180702233412Wnqpz9Z5EP1xh8UJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}